                  <h2 class="hidden">Welcome to Rio Tinto Aluminium</h2>



                  <p><img src="/images/head_welcome.gif" width="544" height="89" alt="The global leader in the aluminium industry" /></p>
                  <p>Rio Tinto Aluminium is one of five product groups <a title="Rio Tinto website (opens in a new window)" href="http://www.riotinto.com/" target="_blank">operated by Rio Tinto</a>, a leading international mining group. We are a global supplier of high quality bauxite, alumina and aluminium.</p>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  

